{"tid":2155924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢三度向梁晃維吐口水襲擊及拳打一學生胸口 判120 小時服務令","createTime":"2020-08-14T06:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:04:32.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab447a87e8a63855789a556c65896b150edc4b5","tid":2155924,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"現任中西區區議員梁晃維去年與一班學生在港鐵葵芳站外派發「三罷」宣傳單張期間，遭一名中年漢三度吐口水襲擊，其中一名男學生更被拳打胸口。涉事的中年漢早前承認兩項普通襲擊罪，西九龍裁判法院主任裁判官羅德泉今日（14日）判處被告 120 小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%88%A4-120-%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%8D%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%2599%2583%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%2590%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2588%25A4-120-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR83u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=216fc0a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%2599%2583%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%2590%2590%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E6%258B%25B3%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%2588%25A4-120-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&h=3e84e144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AA%8D%E5%90%91%E6%A2%81%E6%99%83%E7%B6%AD%E5%90%90%E5%8F%A3%E6%B0%B4-%E6%8B%B3%E6%89%93%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E5%88%A4-120-%E